# Copy to .env.local and adjust. Vite only exposes vars prefixed with VITE_.

# Point the app at the caching proxy instead of OpenF1 directly. The proxy keeps
# your API key server-side and lets one key serve many simultaneous viewers.
# Leave unset to call OpenF1 directly (historical data, no key needed).
# VITE_OPENF1_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8787/v1

# ---- server/proxy.mjs (run with: npm run proxy) ----
# Your OpenF1 sponsor API key — required for LIVE data. Never commit the real key.
# OPENF1_API_KEY=your-key-here
# PORT=8787
# CACHE_TTL_MS=2000
